      "comment": "WOW GIRL (4) was below best last time finishing fifth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Grade 5 win two back at this track. Can turn form around here. CARL BRUCE (1) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a win (17.52) there two back. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. One of the better hopes. SEE RED (8) has missed the frame at her last couple but did finish in the minors in quick time three back (17.53) at this track in a Grade 5. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. KINGSBRAE MAGGIE (3) is building a nice sequence of wins and will be thereabouts again.",
